{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase entitlements to rest breaks at work",
        "additional_details": "People's quality of life does matter, and such changes may also contribute to better and safer production, as well as help employees to feel more appreciated and respected.",
        "background": "Workers, during six hours of toil should be entitled to one 30-minute break and one 10-15 minute break, or within eight hours of toil a 40-minute break and two 10-15 minutes breaks. The current 20 min for 6 hours is inadequate.",
